Description: Flying Desktop - Lightweight launcher with gamepad support
 A lightweight desktop environment for launching applications with
 keyboard and gamepad support. Features include customizable interface,
 layered configuration system, and background image support.
 .
 The application is built as a self-contained binary using PyInstaller,
 minimizing runtime dependencies. It supports launching custom applications
 and provides a simple, full-screen interface suitable for various
 application launching scenarios.
 .
 Configuration is managed through a layered system supporting both
 system-wide and user-specific settings.